{"tid":2164946,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"著名學者戴蒙德警告：中共武力攻台威脅絕不是虛張聲勢","createTime":"2020-08-19T13:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T07:30:14.000Z","uid":279401,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2c1bfb10221decdbaf591858c102d683058ec2","tid":2164946,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:20:30.000Z","msg":"如果認為中共&ldquo;武力統一台灣&rdquo;的說法只是虛張聲勢，那就大錯特錯，是極其危險的。這是世界知名民主理論學者拉里&middot; 戴蒙德 ( Larry Diamond )的警告。<br />\n日前，戴蒙德 (中文名字也叫戴雅門)接受斯坦福大學胡佛研究院的播客(podcast)採訪，進行了名為&ldquo;中國挑戰的過去、現在和未來&rdquo;的談話討論。他指出，美國花了很長時間才把中共顛覆西方民主的行為拼出一幅完整的畫面；美國外交政策和智庫極大低估了中共未來五到十年的危險；中共說要入侵台灣絕不是吹牛。<br />\n他說，&ldquo;儘管希望中共是在虛張聲勢，但是我認為，說出中共虛張聲勢這句話本身是危險的，是錯覺。我們以為他們在香港問題上是這樣，結果不是。他們慢慢地蠶食，一步一步地扼殺了香港的自由&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/larry-diamond-on-china-challenge/5549459.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Flarry-diamond-on-china-challenge%2F5549459.html&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInE8L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=cfb24404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/larry-diamond-on-china-challenge/5549459.html</a>"},{"pid":"aeace00d65929f14b8d8d9869ef014613a9541c1","tid":2164946,"uid":279401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"國家必勝！"},{"pid":"774eca8bc1675aa642f783977ef068b7972f9d88","tid":2164946,"uid":104767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:25:42.000Z","msg":"幾驚你唔打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f273823b11c01e951359b86f947aad71c2103e8","tid":2164946,"uid":189564,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CHUmsu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CHUmsu.jpg&h=5521b333&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0b026e1f2bce7d2a0e722d6df22e660fb4cd5a8","tid":2164946,"uid":1